title: Ooltewah High School vs. Cleveland High School
text: He goes deep for Skyler Davis, and he hauls it in for the touchdown.Cleveland with a shocking 14-0 lead at the half.Third quarter, Owls go with their back-up quarterback in Colin Thurman.Blue Raiders go after him.Ben Wyrick records the sack.Later on, more heat on Thurman.This time it's Zach Willis getting the sack.Cleveland had been out-scored 75-7 in their last two games.But Friday night, they pulled off a stunning 14-7 win over the previously undefeated Owls.
